{"tid":2081471,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"順勢療法/髗骶骨療法/薩滿/其他療法資深用家請進gp不時比意見,25歲胖男,腹瀉,手腳無力,不能上學/班,病齡8年","createTime":"2020-06-27T08:58:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-05T05:43:55.000Z","uid":46752,"like":1,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5e34cc4b7daa0afa5386cadf7db5ad758e3c6efe","tid":2081471,"uid":46752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T08:58:09.000Z","msg":"ct腦之後冇事就要試<br />\n<br />\n25歲胖男，腹瀉，手腳無力，不能上學/班，病齡8年<br />\n<br />\n主訴：<br />\n我的蛋白質類攝取中只選極低脂的食物，如雞胸、極低脂魚柳、蝦。如食物中脂肪比例增加，如生牛肉湯濛（營養師建議吃），吃了有機會肚痛/腹瀉/&ldquo;濟&rdquo;/大便爛（以往出現，現在不敢吃，不確定）。<br />\n<br />\n現史：<br />\n手腳無力至不能自理（程度：煮一人餐），職業治療師診斷我手做重複性動作會累<br />\n手指耐力低<br />\n曾吃粗糧，肚臍上9cm位置頂<br />\n手腳掌出汗，手腳掌冰冷，腳板脫皮<br />\n小便分差，陽痿（連皮/剝皮香蕉硬度）<br />\n<br />\n往史:<br />\n09年9月-11年5月，曾常吃龜苓膏、飲涼茶，以防暗瘡，現回頭看不應吃。有手淫習慣<br />\n12年9月開始手腳無力至今<br />\n14年5月開始嚴重<br />\n6,7月很疲勞仍勉強上學/班，結果更疲勞<br />\n9月起經常腹瀉<br />\n<br />\n家人病歷：<br />\n父：痔瘡<br />\n母：乙型肝炎、小腸氣、割掉口水線有粒嘢<br />\n兄：無<br />\n<br />\n西醫:<br />\n精神科開了aripiprazole 5mg sertraline (hcl) 50mg 各每日半粒<br />\n腦神經內科做了神經傳導檢查，排除了重症肌無力，問他有甚麼其他檢查可做，他說無。<br />\n內分泌科排除了Cushing's syndrome。<br />\n照過胸背頸x光。 <br />\n14年驗出肝酵素高。 <br />\n17年照胃鏡，有胃炎。 脂肪肝。<br />\n<br />\n中醫：<br />\n基本上以以下路線醫好一半，-代表藥後反應<br />\n參苓白朮散-止瀉、有力＞平胃散-大便變完整＞右歸丸贊育丹減約半熟地-吃油少少較不易肚屙＞便秘之後就睇黃志忠-好亂手寫個張＞十全大補-有力<br />\n另外：<br />\n補中益氣湯-有力<br />\n<br />\n病人資料、問診單、舊中藥處方：<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/folderview?id=1w43NYFeh1boJcW3eXLO3aYg490VHeOjU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Ffolderview%3Fid%3D1w43NYFeh1boJcW3eXLO3aYg490VHeOjU&d=mwjAj24IHyfJiBWsHz9aFu2wegjmRFMzjbv%2B285MJ7g%3D&h=9a05af93\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/folderview?id=1w43NYFeh1boJcW3eXLO3aYg490VHeOjU</a><br />\n<br />\ntg group/ tg:<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/E38pyFcoqheNbzSaruFL-Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FE38pyFcoqheNbzSaruFL-Q&d=mwjAj24IHyfJiBWsHz9aFu2wegjmRFMzjbv%2B285MJ7g%3D&h=1acd8505\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/E38pyFcoqheNbzSaruFL-Q</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/Usernamennn\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FUsernamennn&d=mwjAj24IHyfJiBWsHz9aFu2wegjmRFMzjbv%2B285MJ7g%3D&h=fe706b58\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/Usernamennn</a><br />\nfb messager:<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.me/seek.chinesemedicine.1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.me%2Fseek.chinesemedicine.1&d=mwjAj24IHyfJiBWsHz9aFu2wegjmRFMzjbv%2B285MJ7g%3D&h=19d4f895\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.me/seek.chinesemedicine.1</a><br />\n<br />\n跪求介紹治療師<br />\n請問<br />\n1他有沒醫好過手腳無力及不能自理（程度不能煮一人餐）？<br />\n2他有沒醫好過以下情況？&ldquo;我現在只吃白灼雞胸。以往，如果食物中加了少少油烹調，吃了有機會肚痛/濟/大便爛。&rdquo;<br />\n3他醫好過甚麼棘手個案<br />\n4介不介意分享你甚麼病<br />\n5你看了幾長時間病？<br />\n<br />\n待辦診治：要求西醫照腦<br />\n髗骶骨療法<br />\n薩滿<br />\n接地氣<br />\n一堆中醫(趙文偉、孔華etc)<br />\n吳神父按摩<br />\n<br />\n未試，不覺得有用：原始點<br />\n醫療靈媒"},{"pid":"0f53bbfc6fde470fe9b6617c92924969eaf764ea","tid":2081471,"uid":46752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T06:12:25.000Z","msg":"."},{"pid":"2abc29eaa9f88e4f23f405a3b6be10de74108d61","tid":2081471,"uid":46752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T06:16:22.000Z","msg":"."},{"pid":"24869744e8068b82404a8121abc5b264799d555c","tid":2081471,"uid":46752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T03:18:31.000Z","msg":"."},{"pid":"9fb5b96919f7ffb00f9fdd50d65e56a02c95089b","tid":2081471,"uid":48767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T03:53:17.000Z","msg":"自己俾錢照pet scan mri啦"},{"pid":"3dbc6681f964d819cec4201dbbf27c0ee6e25366","tid":2081471,"uid":46752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9fb5b96919f7ffb00f9fdd50d65e56a02c95089b","tid":2081471,"uid":48767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T03:53:17.000Z","msg":"自己俾錢照pet scan mri啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T05:26:53.000Z","msg":"精神藥有d效試真d先<br />\n叫咗醫生轉介<br />\n<br />\n轉po<br />\n薩滿/醫療靈媒/文王殿/音叉/生物共振/髗骶骨用家請進tg gp比意見,不能上學/班,病8年,腹瀉,手腳無力,25歲胖男<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2094795\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2094795</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b64d804effb52345a434cb4c367cfc6c59b4b724","tid":2081471,"uid":1025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T05:39:25.000Z","msg":"第幾個post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"070a02fbc40fcc883bbbc4466ede6d53a0ab6c5e","tid":2081471,"uid":190264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b64d804effb52345a434cb4c367cfc6c59b4b724","tid":2081471,"uid":1025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T05:39:25.000Z","msg":"第幾個post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T05:42:06.000Z","msg":"樓主無野做<br />\n開post志在屌下人出氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4be6601b0a999a9d99196b82c73a83a1afa43264","tid":2081471,"uid":1025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"070a02fbc40fcc883bbbc4466ede6d53a0ab6c5e","tid":2081471,"uid":190264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b64d804effb52345a434cb4c367cfc6c59b4b724","tid":2081471,"uid":1025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T05:39:25.000Z","msg":"第幾個post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T05:42:06.000Z","msg":"樓主無野做<br />\n開post志在屌下人出氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T05:43:55.000Z","msg":"記得睇過幾次最後係度屌鳩d人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}